name: To Catch a Smuggler
overview: Millions enter the US through airports each year, and hid amongst them are a stream of contraband ill intentions. Defending our borders are the vigilant men and women of the Department of Homeland Security, whose agencies make up a three-tiered defense of America’s airports. DHS will stop at nothing to catch a smuggler.

episodes.name: Internal Investigation
episodes.overview: MIA CBP investigates a traveler suspected of smuggling drugs internally. JFK HSI conducts a controlled delivery of ecstasy to Wall Street in Manhattan.

episodes.name: Club Drugs and Party People
episodes.overview: MIA CBP finds a package of ecstasy, which leads to a controlled delivery and arrest. JFK CBP questions a traveler connected to known drug smugglers.

episodes.name: Suspicious Suitcase
episodes.overview: MIA CBP searches a traveler with a suspicious story and suitcase. JFK HSI works to open pistons filled with drugs, which leads to a controlled delivery.

episodes.name: Cocaine Crackdown
episodes.overview: LAX CBP monitors suspicious bags. At JFK, officers find bottles of liquid cocaine. MIA HSI conducts a controlled delivery of cocaine found in paintings.

episodes.name: Smuggle Once, Smuggle Twice?
episodes.overview: An international operation to stop arms trafficking networks leads HSI and Argentinian authorities to raid the homes of possible weapons traffickers.

episodes.name: Drugs, Guns and Money
episodes.overview: CBP JFK finds drugs concealed in cans, HSI Miami stops a date rape drug from hitting the streets, and CBP LAX suspects a woman of marriage fraud.

episodes.name: Cocaine Sausages
episodes.overview: CBP gets the truth out of a suspicious Nigerian passenger arriving at LAX. HSI zeroes in on food couriers smuggling narcotics into JFK.

episodes.name: Decoys, Diversions and Drug Busts
episodes.overview: HSI and CBP team up to stop drugs from coming through JFK, and in Miami, a passenger with ties to a known drug smuggler is questioned.

episodes.name: Mama's Meth
episodes.overview: HSI conducts a controlled delivery of meth, while CBP deals with an unruly passenger.

episodes.name: The Coke Inside
episodes.overview: Using an undercover agent, HSI finds a meth smuggler in Atlanta. CBP officers catch a passenger in New York with drugs inserted inside of her.

episodes.name: Party Drugs
episodes.overview: CBP looks out for party drugs, prostitutes and counterfeit goods entering Miami during Super Bowl. HSI tracks the case of a drug-filled car battery.

episodes.name: Endangered and Smuggled
episodes.overview: CBP investigates a trend of cocaine concealed in coffee bags, and cracks down on a series of wildlife trafficking crimes.

episodes.name: Hidden Compartments
episodes.overview: HSI takes to the streets of Brooklyn to arrest the person picking up a suitcase of cocaine. CBP catches a man who has swallowed 85 pellets of cocaine.

episodes.name: Stash House Takedown
episodes.overview: HSI disrupt a transnational meth ring and CBP seize a huge shipment of illegal shark fins.

episodes.name: Coke, Cakes and Cash
episodes.overview: HSI pursues a case of cocaine-filled cakes across state lines, and CBP seizes more than $100,000 of undeclared currency.

episodes.name: Dark Web and Liquid Drugs
episodes.overview: HSI takes down a suspected weapons trafficker with ties to organized crime. CBP is on alert for popular club drugs being concealed in liquid form.

episodes.name: Cocaine Shoes
episodes.overview: Hidden among the millions who enter the U.S. through JFK, MIA and ATL is dangerous contraband. DHS will stop at nothing to catch these smugglers.

episodes.name: Lockdown Lockup
episodes.overview: CBP finds a smuggler of so-called “crazy pills” at JFK and responds to the COVID-19 crisis on the southern border, seizing over 800 lbs of meth.

episodes.name: Fentanyl Within
episodes.overview: CBP Nogales busts a man internally smuggling fentanyl from Mexico. HSI delves into the dark web to stop a deadly party drug linked to overdoses.

episodes.name: Mobile Meth
episodes.overview: CBP New York discovers priceless shipments of looted ancient artifacts. CBP Newark intercepts stolen luxury cars headed for the overseas black market.

episodes.name: Express Delivery Ecstasy
episodes.overview: CBP finds multiple doses of lethal fentanyl hidden within passenger cars, and CBP Newark searches for an illegal stowaway onboard a cargo ship

episodes.name: Mega Millions Meth Stash
episodes.overview: While inspecting commercial cargo from Mexico, Laredo CBP discovers liquid meth concealed within paint buckets. In Atlanta, HSI conducts a controlled delivery of an air conditioner filled with 2 kgs of meth.

episodes.name: Meth Lab Takedown
episodes.overview: HSI tails a truck loaded with narcotics to a meth compound near Los Angeles, and CBP discovers fentanyl and meth in cars using trusted traveler lanes.

episodes.name: Smuggled and Muzzled
episodes.overview: CBP Nogales uncovers cocaine in the bumper of a car crossing from Mexico, and CBP Atlanta stops a woman smuggling underaged puppies from Brazil.

episodes.name: Jungle Stash
episodes.overview: CBP hunts for drug runners off the coast and in the jungles of Puerto Rico, while CBP Laredo seizes 130 lbs of marijuana hidden inside BBQ grills.

episodes.name: Bunked in a Trunk
episodes.overview: Officers confront human smuggling at the border and nab a car loaded with fentanyl

episodes.name: Smorgasbord of Smack
episodes.overview: HSI nabs car loaded with a medley of narcotics, while CBP seizes looted ancient artifacts.

episodes.name: Killer Ketamine
episodes.overview: CBP screens for club drugs hidden in toiletries, while HSI uncovers meth buried in garlic.

episodes.name: Guns of New York
episodes.overview: HSI busts an illegal gun operation in NYC, while CBP confronts a meth surge from Mexico.

episodes.name: Gas Tank Meth
episodes.overview: HSI snags a truck loaded with meth, while CBP’s beagles sniff out contraband.

episodes.name: Powdered Rims
episodes.overview: HSI finds cocaine-filled tire rims in cargo and nabs a car loaded with meth and fentanyl.

episodes.name: Million Dollar Ride
episodes.overview: HSI seizes counterfeit cash and vax cards. CBP pulls 205 kilos of meth out of one car.

episodes.name: Dope on a Rope
episodes.overview: CBP pulls a line of meth from a gas tank and stops an internal body carrier with fentanyl.

episodes.name: Six Million Dollar Seizure
episodes.overview: HSI takes down a multi-million-dollar, transnational smuggling ring of airline employees.

episodes.name: Drug Boat Bust
episodes.overview: CBP seizes counterfeit medications, and HSI pursues a series of maritime smuggling cases.

episodes.name: Cocaine Snapper
episodes.overview: HSI Miami catches a shipment of cocaine-filled fish, CBP takes on human smuggling at the border, and agriculture specialists in ATL search passengers.

episodes.name: Talibani Treasure Trove
episodes.overview: HSI busts a ketamine smuggler in Miami, K9s sniff out fentanyl in San Diego and JFK officers uncover ancient gold looted from Afghanistan.

episodes.name: Tunnel from Tijuana
episodes.overview: AMO Puerto Rico sinks a marine smuggling op. In San Diego, HSI shuts down a tunnel dug under the border by a cartel, and a CBP K9 finds drugs in a car.

episodes.name: Dark Net Dragnet
episodes.overview: HSI busts a notorious dark web trafficker in France, while CBP screens travelers for fentanyl in AZ and airline passengers for illicit cash in FL.

episodes.name: Blow Overboard
episodes.overview: AMO agents in Puerto Rico chase smugglers at sea who toss their load overboard, while meth pops out of a car after a fender bender in El Paso.

episodes.name: Coke on the Water
episodes.overview: HSI stakes out a cartel handoff of cocaine in Texas, while CBP finds coke hidden on ships in Miami and screens for duty violations at JFK.

episodes.name: MDMA on the Move
episodes.overview: HSI tracks an ecstasy package through Chicago, while CBP finds fentanyl abandoned in a bathroom in Texas and searches travelers for narcotics at JFK.

episodes.name: Meth in the City
episodes.overview: HSI executes a controlled delivery of meth in Brooklyn, while CBP finds 2C on partiers in Florida and a vehicle bursting with meth in San Diego.

episodes.name: Guac and Coke
episodes.overview: CBP finds 142 kilos of coke in a shipment of avocados in Florida, while CBP, HSI and Border Patrol pursue human smuggling leads in Texas.

episodes.name: It's Raining Meth
episodes.overview: HSI executes a controlled delivery of ketamine in Queens, NY, while CBP recovers stolen artifacts in Miami and finds a mega shipment of meth at LAX.

episodes.name: Boatloads of Coke
episodes.overview: CBP finds an SUV loaded with meth at the border and counterfeit cash in Atlanta. Operation Blood Moon yields 2000 kilos of cocaine in Puerto Rico.

episodes.name: Hot Drugs
episodes.overview: In the heat of El Paso, CBP stops 30 kilos of cocaine from crossing the border. Officers intercept $150K worth of illegal pills in Philadelphia.

episodes.name: Popped for Pills
episodes.overview: CBP and HSI target 25,000 ecstasy pills intercepted in Germany bound for PHL. CBP finds $143K of meth at the border, and an ancient statue at JFK.

episodes.name: Bananas and Blow
episodes.overview: At Philly Seaport, CBP finds containers loaded with coke. In El Paso, the cartel thwarts HSI’s controlled delivery of 40 kilos of marijuana.

episodes.name: The Coke Eater
episodes.overview: CBP questions a man traveling from Panama suspected of ingesting pellets of coke. PR AMO agents track down a boat loaded with $51M worth of cocaine.

episodes.name: Dope in the Hood
episodes.overview: HSI in California organizes undercover drug buys with numerous traffickers. CBP El Paso intercepts Coyotes heading back into Mexico.

episodes.name: Freeway Meth
episodes.overview: HSI in San Diego tracks a vehicle stuffed with meth all the way to Long Beach. CBP & HSI in Philly test a new drug detection device.

episodes.name: Ice Cold Cocaine
episodes.overview: CBP in El Paso finds $1M of cocaine hidden in a refrigerated cargo truck. LA HSI executes controlled delivery and arrests recipient of date rape drug.

episodes.name: Junk in the Trunk
episodes.overview: An HSI stakeout leads to nearly $500K of meth and fentanyl in San Diego. CBP finds concealed cash and a carload of cocaine at the El Paso border.

episodes.name: Asleep on Lots of Coke
episodes.overview: PR AMO team hunts down boat loaded with $41M of coke. CBP gets a tip about money smugglers and finds cocaine and people inside car trunks.

episodes.name: To the Grinder
episodes.overview: HSI Orange County performs 3 undercover drug stings with multiple arrests. CBP finds cocaine hidden under a vehicle's backseat in Rio Grande Valley.

episodes.name: Money Dog
episodes.overview: CBP's K9 sniffs out stacks of hidden cash in Atlanta. HSI air surveillance tracks a multi-level drug deal in San Diego, seizing $2 million of dope.

episodes.name: Fentanyl Express
episodes.overview: After fentanyl bust at JFK, CBP blitzes food courier bags. SD HSI arrests dealer trying to ship kilo of fentanyl to NY. CBP RGV finds meth and weed.

episodes.name: Gold Diggers
episodes.overview: HSI helps Colombian National Police take down illegal gold mining ring. CBP finds almost $1.5 million cartel drug haul at RGV port in Texas.

episodes.name: Meth Magnets and Dirty Money
episodes.overview: HSI runs multiple money laundering stings in Chicago. CBP has two of the largest crystal meth seizures in LAX history.

episodes.name: Cocaine Rides in the Crew Cab
episodes.overview: HSI runs a human trafficking sting at a KC hotel. CBP in Philly is on the hunt for a passenger suspected of making terroristic threats in the US.

episodes.name: Cocaine Leaks and Ancient Greeks
episodes.overview: HSI San Diego runs down a drug smuggler during a parking lot cocaine transfer. CBP at JFK discovers gold coins and ancient artifacts in mail parcels.

episodes.name: Not My Meth
episodes.overview: A mother crossing by car with her kids is caught smuggling cocaine in El Paso. AMO shoots out the engine of a boat loaded with coke in Puerto Rico.

episodes.name: Pots of Coke
episodes.overview: HSI tracks a shipment of $12.6 million worth of cocaine hidden in gardening pots. CBP seizes illicit ammo and cash traveling to Mexico.

episodes.name: Coke and the Kids
episodes.overview: HSI chases fleeing coke smugglers near a school. CBP finds shipments of pills, ketamine, & counterfeit cash, and stops knockoff shoes at the border.

episodes.name: New Drug on the Block
episodes.overview: HSI Miami encounters mysterious new drug; CBP finds invasive snails in mail.

episodes.name: My Big Fat Weed Run
episodes.overview: CBP finds weed worth $200k inside a passenger's luggage. HSI in Colombia raids apartment filled with counterfeit sneakers. CBP finds coke in a bumper.

episodes.name: Coked-up Oatmeal
episodes.overview: Undercover HSI Agents bust multiple drug traffickers seizing 30 kilos of meth and fentanyl. CBP finds cocaine hidden in oatmeal and medicine boxes.

episodes.name: Flesh, Bones, Ketamine and Drones
episodes.overview: CBP discovers ketamine and human remains in packages from Europe. U.S. Border Patrol intercepts smugglers bringing migrants across the Rio Grande.

episodes.name: Unholy Guacamole
episodes.overview: HSI finds cocaine hidden in frozen avocado paste; CBP recovers stolen cars.

episodes.name: Weed In, Weed Out
episodes.overview: Border Patrol chases suspect fleeing arrest; CBP stops weed leaving U.S.

episodes.name: Blitzed at the Border
episodes.overview: CBP in McAllen faces a possible bomb; HSI arrests fentanyl traffickers.

episodes.name: Spiced and Loaded
episodes.overview: HSI tails vehicle transporting meth; CBP seizes looted Ukrainian relics.

episodes.name: These Bedsheets Are Dope!
episodes.overview: CBP Dulles finds outbound drugs; Border Patrol tracks human smugglers.

episodes.name: No Rest for the Wicked
episodes.overview: A 48-hour sting leads HSI to a stash house; CBP finds drugs in gas tanks.

episodes.name: Drugs, Bugs and the Big Buy-Bust
episodes.overview: Rookie CBP officers find multiple drugs; HSI runs a buy-bust operation.

episodes.name: Meth Inside the Machine
episodes.overview: HSI finds overcrowded human stash houses; CBP discovers meth in machinery.
